
     * format original dial string
     * 1) convert international dialing prefix "+" to
     *    string specified per region
     *
     * 2) handle corner cases for PAUSE/WAIT dialing:
     *
     *    If PAUSE/WAIT sequence at the end, ignore them.
     *
